        <div class="model-map-block">
            <div class="callout-wrapper">
                <div class="callout-box">
                    <strong>Note:</strong> This page provides a comprehensive mapping between the Logical Model for Social History and the FHIR profiles defined in this Patient Summary implementation guide.
                </div>
