        <h3 id="overview">Social History Mapping -&gt; FHIR Profiles (CZ PS)</h3>

        <p>
            Below is a browsable diagram showing how the Social History model is realized by the HL7 FHIR profiles defined in this guide. The mapping covers substance use including alcohol, tobacco, drugs, and other addictions.
        </p>

        <h4 id="model">Model Overview</h4>
        <p>{% include PS_SocialHistory-map.svg %}</p>

        <div class="table-wrap">
            <strong>Mapping Context</strong>

            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Source logical model:</strong>
                    <a href="StructureDefinition-LogSocialHistoryCzEn.html">LogSocialHistoryCzEn</a>
                </li>

                <li>
                    <strong>Main target profile:</strong>
                    <a href="StructureDefinition-cz-composition-ps.html">cz-composition-ps</a>
                </li>

            </ul>

        </div>

